d grow near the boundary\nbetween GI active and inactive regions. We discuss the possible implications of\nthese rings for gas giant planet formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Jul 2004 23:09:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
